Name: megatunix
Summary: Megatunix. Megasquirt and Megasquirt-II Configuration Program.
Version: @VERSION@
Release: 1
Copyright: GPL
Group: Applications/Engineering
Source: megatunix-@VERSION@.tar.gz
BuildRequires: flex, libxml2-devel, libglade2-devel, gtkglext-devel
Requires: libxml2, libglade2, gtkglext
BuildRoot: %{_tmppath}/%{name}-buildroot
Packager: Eduardo Kaftanski <e@nn.cl>

%description
MegaTunix is the ONLY cross platform tuning software for the MegaSquirt
family of DIY Fuel Injection (and ignition) ECU's.  It currently supports
All Stock B&G Firmwares (1.0-3.01), All F&H DualTable Firmwares (0.90-1.02),
All MegaSquirtnEDIS Firmwares (0.1-3.008), MegaSquirtnSpark (3.x) and full
support is in place for MegaSquirtnSpark-Extra 029x and newer.  ECU detection
is completely automatic, and the gui will self adapt to the detected firmware.

All firmware features are supported, including very extensive datalogging 
capabilities, ecu backup and restore, and Table export/import.

MegaTunix is extensible for user modified firmware, by utilizing the Glade
Gui designer, and a simple text editor.

MegaTunix is writtenand maintained by David J. Andruczyk, copyright 2009.
%prep
%setup -q
#%patch -p1 -b .buildroot

%build
./configure --prefix=$RPM_BUILD_ROOT/usr
make RPM_OPT_FLAGS="$RPM_OPT_FLAGS"

%install
rm -rf $RPM_BUILD_ROOT

make install

%clean
rm -rf $RPM_BUILD_ROOT

%files
%defattr(-,root,root)

/usr/bin/megatunix
/usr/share/MegaTunix

